{"tid":512759,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"下月初或迎寒潮！跌至9°C機率幾大？","createTime":"2017-12-28T22:51:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T00:30:14.000Z","uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"99120124c26d6a8b73739704a5381e5489139fdd","tid":512759,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T22:51:37.000Z","msg":"除夕（31日）早上，本港會明顯轉涼，天文台預計市區氣溫會由周六下午的21&deg;C，跌至周日早上的15&deg;C。隨後幾日的氣溫雖稍為回升，但至下周後期又再度下降，暫料下周末（6日）降至14&deg;C。不過低處未算低，天文台電腦預報顯示，下月初市區氣溫暫有30至40%機會，跌至9至11&deg;C的寒冷程度。<br />\n<br />\n由電腦直接輸出、未經人手修正的天文台市區低溫概率預報指，本港市區氣溫會由下周五（5日）開始顯著下降，再下周日（7日）最大機會跌至介乎9至11&deg;C，惟機率只有30至40%，反映不確定因素頗大。概率預報每天約於中午更新一次，平均誤差約為一至兩度左右。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/29/065130_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F29%2F065130_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=cd1c2269&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f57a4830dcec9fce00f03fcde88f882741d58ae","tid":512759,"uid":154800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T22:52:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57636019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57636019&d=xdNJ0C%2BU0PNblibMaYokVzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=7a8081da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171229%2F57636019&h=5a97a10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171229/57636019</a>"},{"pid":"df4866072405c08d0091c6d4374247db2f3c5bb4","tid":512759,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T00:30:14.000Z","msg":"電腦分析，65%係7，35%係J，唔係7就係J"}]}